high_descs: Turn and walk to the left side of the tv stand.
Pick up the bowl that is on the tv stand behind the tv.
Turn around and walk to the bedroom. Walk to the shelf that is on the left side of the bed and against the wall.
Place the bowl on the second shelf on the left side of the shelves.
Remove the credit card from the third shelf.
Put the credit card in the bowl that is on the self.
anns.task_desc: Take the bowl to the shelf and put the credit card in it.

high_descs: Walk forward to the TV stand
Pick up the bowl from the TV stand
Turn around and walk into the bedroom and face towards the shelf in the corner
Put the bowl down on the left side of the shelf
Pick up the credit card from the shelf
Put the credit card in the bowl
anns.task_desc: Put the credit card in the bowl on the shelf

high_descs: Turn left to reach the TV stand.
Pick up the bowl from the TV stand.
Turn around and head right to reach the shelf.
Put the bowl in the top left shelf.
Pick up the credit card from the shelf below.
Put the credit card in the bowl above.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with the credit card on the top shelf.
